{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:1","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.008.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. 2 Co 8. (Pr 19:17. H\u00e9 13:16. 1 Ti 6:17-19. Ph 4:15-19. 1 Jn 3:16-18.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Il est superflu que je vous \u00e9crive touchant l\u2019assistance destin\u00e9e aux saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24","name":"2 Corinthiens 8:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.8.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:2","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Je connais, en effet, votre bonne volont\u00e9, dont je me glorifie pour vous aupr\u00e8s des Mac\u00e9doniens, en d\u00e9clarant que l\u2019Acha\u00efe est pr\u00eate depuis l\u2019ann\u00e9e derni\u00e8re; et ce z\u00e8le de votre part a stimul\u00e9 le plus grand nombre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:3","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>J\u2019envoie les fr\u00e8res, afin que l\u2019\u00e9loge que nous avons fait de vous ne soit pas r\u00e9duit \u00e0 n\u00e9ant sur ce point-l\u00e0, et que vous soyez pr\u00eats, comme je l\u2019ai dit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:4","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Je ne voudrais pas, si les Mac\u00e9doniens m\u2019accompagnent et ne vous trouvent pas pr\u00eats, que cette assurance tourn\u00e2t \u00e0 notre confusion, pour ne pas dire \u00e0 la v\u00f4tre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:5","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>J\u2019ai donc jug\u00e9 n\u00e9cessaire d\u2019inviter les fr\u00e8res \u00e0 se rendre auparavant chez vous, et \u00e0 s\u2019occuper de votre lib\u00e9ralit\u00e9 d\u00e9j\u00e0 promise, afin qu\u2019elle soit pr\u00eate, de mani\u00e8re \u00e0 \u00eatre une lib\u00e9ralit\u00e9, et non un acte d\u2019avarice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:6","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Sachez-le, celui qui s\u00e8me peu moissonnera peu, et celui qui s\u00e8me abondamment moissonnera abondamment.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:7","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Que chacun donne comme il l\u2019a r\u00e9solu en son c\u0153ur, sans tristesse ni contrainte; car Dieu aime celui qui donne avec joie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:8","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et Dieu peut vous combler de toutes sortes de gr\u00e2ces, afin que, poss\u00e9dant toujours en toutes choses de quoi satisfaire \u00e0 tous vos besoins, vous ayez encore en abondance pour toute bonne \u0153uvre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:9","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Il a fait des largesses, il a donn\u00e9 aux indigents;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sa justice subsiste \u00e0 jamais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:10","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Celui qui<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Fournit de la semence au semeur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et du pain pour sa nourriture,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">vous fournira et vous multipliera la semence, et il augmentera les fruits de votre justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:11","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Vous serez de la sorte enrichis \u00e0 tous \u00e9gards pour toute esp\u00e8ce de lib\u00e9ralit\u00e9s qui, par notre moyen, feront offrir \u00e0 Dieu des actions de gr\u00e2ces.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:12","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Car le secours de cette assistance non seulement pourvoit aux besoins des saints, mais il est encore une source abondante de nombreuses actions de gr\u00e2ces envers Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:13","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>En consid\u00e9ration de ce secours dont ils font l\u2019exp\u00e9rience, ils glorifient Dieu de votre ob\u00e9issance dans la profession de l\u2019\u00c9vangile de Christ, et de la lib\u00e9ralit\u00e9 de vos dons envers eux et envers tous;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:14","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.009.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>ils prient pour vous, parce qu\u2019ils vous aiment \u00e0 cause de la gr\u00e2ce \u00e9minente que Dieu vous a faite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 9:15","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"2Cor.9.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Gr\u00e2ces soient rendues \u00e0 Dieu pour son don ineffable!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6eab605.04723699');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6eab605.04723699\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb6eab605.04723699","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb6eab605.04723699'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6eab605.04723699\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}